lead_paragraph: Olympic pole vault champion Jenn Suhr does not plan to compete in next month's IAAF indoor championships even though she has just broken her world indoor record, the American said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Record-Breaking Suhr to Miss World Indoor Championships
